com.newrelic.graphql.schema.scalars

Class PredefinedScalars

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.newrelic.graphql.schema.scalars.PredefinedScalars

  • public final class PredefinedScalars
extends java.lang.Object
    Registration for all of the predefined scalars that ship with this library.

    By default these are included in GraphQL execution instances built via SimpleGraphQLBuilder.

    Use the addScalar static function during class definition to include additional types.
